entries.MST_FROGATE10_DESC:
A trial program that tests how much damage
you can inflict in a short amount of time.
Try to make your attacks more efficient!
entries.MST_FROGATE11_DESC:
This trial program will test your limits
until you use the last of your strength.
Consider your options and go forth with a solid group!
entries.MST_FROGATE12_DESC:
A trial program exclusive to male Units.
Strong opponents await to test
every last drop of your potential.
entries.MST_FROGATE13_DESC:
A trial program exclusive to female Units.
Strong opponents await to test
every last drop of your potential.
entries.MST_FROGATE14_DESC:
A trial program made for Grand Gaia adventurers.
Here you will face the gods anew as a test of your true power.
entries.MST_FROGATE15_DESC:
A trial program made for Ishgria adventurers.
Here you will face the demons anew as a test of your true power.
entries.MST_FROGATE16_DESC:
A trial program where you fight to the
end using only Thunder and Light type Units.
Test your limits under these demanding restrictions!
entries.MST_FROGATE17_DESC:
A trial program where you fight to the
end using only Fire and Dark type Units.
Test your limits under these demanding restrictions!
entries.MST_FROGATE18_DESC: A trial program where you fight to the end using only Water and Earth type Units. Test your limits under these demanding restrictions!
entries.MST_FROGATE1_DESC:
There's nothing special about Noel's first implementation,
but the enemies do grow stronger over time,
so even novices may challenge it.
entries.MST_FROGATE2_DESC:
A new trial program for challengers who seek basic battle practice.
Even new Summoners can use it to test their strength
and collect experience.
entries.MST_FROGATE3_DESC:
A trial program exclusive to Earth Units.
How will you beat your foes under such conditions?
Here, your summoning skills will be tested.

entries.MST_FROGATE9_DESC:
A trial program exclusive to 6-star rarity Units or below.
Can you use your maxed out Units
to the full extent of their potential?
